      <title>贷款紧缩导致泰国 2024 年汽车销量下降 26%，实现“亚洲底特律”目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/thailand-s-detroit-of-asia-nickname-hit-as-car-sales-fall-26-on-loan-squeeze</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国国内汽车销量跌至 14 年来的最低水平，损害了其作为“亚洲底特律”的声誉，因为银行贷款审批收紧和家庭债务高企抑制了汽车需​​求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/thailand-s-detroit-of-asia-nickname-hit-as-car-sales-fall-26-on-loan-squeeze</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:21:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ING 出售俄罗斯业务将损失 7 亿欧元利润</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ing-to-take-700-million-profit-hit-to-sell-russian-business</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰国际集团（ING Groep NV）同意以未公开的价格出售其俄罗斯业务，并在其入侵乌克兰三年后退出俄罗斯，导致其利润损失 7 亿欧元（7.3 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ing-to-take-700-million-profit-hit-to-sell-russian-business</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:04:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港费用下降反映银行业竞争加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/banks-compete-for-catl-listing-big-china-ipos-in-hong-kong-with-cheap-fees</link>
      <description><![CDATA[宁德时代科技股份有限公司即将进行大规模上市，可能募资逾 50 亿美元，这类交易可以为香港等低迷的市场注入急需的活力。但这很快就成为华尔街银行的头疼事。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/banks-compete-for-catl-listing-big-china-ipos-in-hong-kong-with-cheap-fees</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:03:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贷款机构 Colesco 首项战略融资突破 8 亿欧元里程碑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/lender-colesco-tops-800-million-milestone-for-first-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Colesco 是一家致力于可持续投资的私人贷款公司，在私人信贷基金经理探索 ESG 投资之际，该公司已为其首次募集了超过 8 亿欧元（8.39 亿美元）的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/lender-colesco-tops-800-million-milestone-for-first-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税和 DeepSeek 波动令亚洲各地货币交易员困惑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/asia-hedge-funds-stumped-on-tariff-deepseek-currency-whiplash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[市场参与者表示，关税风险上升、科技领域可能出现的“斯普尼克时刻”以及假期临近，让亚洲各地的对冲基金和其他货币交易商不知道该下什么赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/asia-hedge-funds-stumped-on-tariff-deepseek-currency-whiplash</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 06:46:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>意大利公司获得凯雷现金并涉嫌支付游艇和酒庄费用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/italy-firm-got-carlyle-cash-and-allegedly-paid-for-yacht-winery</link>
      <description><![CDATA[2020 年，凯雷集团 (Carlyle Group Inc.) 同意向位于威尼斯附近的家族造纸和包装公司 Pro-Gest SpA 提供约 2 亿欧元（2.1 亿美元）的私人债券，这似乎是一场低风险的赌注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/italy-firm-got-carlyle-cash-and-allegedly-paid-for-yacht-winery</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三位澳新银行信贷交易员离职加入渣打银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/a-trio-of-anz-credit-traders-depart-to-join-standard-chartered</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，澳新银行集团控股有限公司的一些高级信贷交易员将离开这家澳大利亚银行，转投渣打银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/a-trio-of-anz-credit-traders-depart-to-join-standard-chartered</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 04:27:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银即将与印度财富管理公司 360 One 达成协议以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ubs-nears-deal-with-india-wealth-firm-360-one-for-growth-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团 (UBS Group AG) 正在与印度 360 One WAM Ltd. 进行深入谈判，该交易将增强该瑞士银行在该国蓬勃发展的财富市场的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/ubs-nears-deal-with-india-wealth-firm-360-one-for-growth-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 02:57:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
