      <title>市场权衡特朗普最新关税威胁，黄金持稳</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-as-markets-weigh-latest-trump-tariff-threats</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员们权衡唐纳德·特朗普总统的最新关税威胁，同时全球科技股崩盘导致股市阴云笼罩，金价在周一大幅下跌之后趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/gold-xauusd-holds-decline-as-markets-weigh-latest-trump-tariff-threats</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 00:52:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：特朗普誓言实施“大幅”关税，美元上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示希望实施“更大”的普遍关税，美元随之上涨。由于对人工智能行业高估值的担忧持续到第二天，大多数亚洲股市下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 22:48:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
